# Secrets now live in the macOS keychain, not here. Store them with:
#   ./set-secret.sh SUPABASE_KEY
#   ./set-secret.sh BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN
# (SUPABASE_URL is already stored.) This .env is an OPTIONAL per-run override only;
# if present its values take precedence over the keychain. Keep it gitignored.
